title: Santa Cruz Skateboards: Down Under Statement
description:
The Santa Cruz Skateboards squad packed up and headed Down Under! Road life Down Under can get hectic, but the SC Team held it together and handled biz traveling across the continent putting on demo's, chasing 'roos, and shutting down spots along the way!
Sometimes...skateboarding doesn't even involve skateboarding.

Filmed by: Joe Perrin/Gavin Sean Denike
